---
import { Card, CardContent } from "@workspace/ui/components/card"
import { Badge } from "@workspace/ui/components/badge"
---

<section id="problem" class="relative py-16 md:py-24">
  <!-- Subtle glow -->
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0"
    style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 40% at 70% 30%, oklch(0.58 0.22 27 / 0.04) 0%, transparent 70%);"
  ></div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-6">
    <div class="mb-8 md:mb-16">
      <Badge variant="outline" className="mb-4">The Challenge</Badge>
      <h2 class="max-w-2xl font-display text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground md:text-5xl">
        The Global Impact of Biofouling
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl text-base text-muted-foreground md:text-lg">
        Marine biofouling on ship hulls and offshore structures leads to
        increased drag, higher fuel consumption, elevated emissions, and
        significant maintenance costs.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <Card className="group relative overflow-hidden border-none bg-gradient-to-br from-card to-card/50 ring-1 ring-border/50 transition-all hover:ring-primary/30">
        <CardContent className="flex flex-col gap-3 pt-2">
          <div class="flex size-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-destructive/10">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="size-6 text-destructive" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"></line><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="font-display text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground md:text-5xl">$31B</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            Annual cost in increased fuel consumption from hull biofouling worldwide
          </div>
        </CardContent>
      </Card>

      <Card className="group relative overflow-hidden border-none bg-gradient-to-br from-card to-card/50 ring-1 ring-border/50 transition-all hover:ring-primary/30">
        <CardContent className="flex flex-col gap-3 pt-2">
          <div class="flex size-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-chart-1/10">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="size-6 text-chart-1" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20V10"></path><path d="M18 20V4"></path><path d="M6 20v-4"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="font-display text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground md:text-5xl">40%</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            Increase in fuel consumption caused by biofouling on vessel hulls
          </div>
        </CardContent>
      </Card>

      <Card className="group relative overflow-hidden border-none bg-gradient-to-br from-card to-card/50 ring-1 ring-border/50 transition-all hover:ring-primary/30">
        <CardContent className="flex flex-col gap-3 pt-2">
          <div class="flex size-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-destructive/10">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="size-6 text-destructive" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"></path><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"></line><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"></line></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="font-display text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground md:text-5xl">90%</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            Of coatings rely on toxic biocides or PFAS facing increasing regulatory pressure
          </div>
        </CardContent>
      </Card>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
